Package com.cscguru.client.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClickable
    Provides a way to interact with mouse events.
    IDrawable
    Simple interface for objects that can be drawn to the screen.
    ISolid
    Interface for objects that can collide (is solid).
    ITipped
    Interface for tool-tipped items.
    IUpdatable
    Interface used for items that need updates (animations, day/night cycles, etc).
